OL,3,CSir Quentin Blake unveils mural ahead
OL,4,Cof illustration centre opening
OL,6,FChildren's author and illustrator Sir
OL,7,FQuentin Blake has unveiled a mural at
OL,8,Fhis centre for illustration ahead of
OL,9,Fthe venue's opening.
OL,11,FThe Quentin Blake Centre for
OL,12,FIllustration is set to open at a
OL,13,Fheritage site in Clerkenwell, central
OL,14,FLondon, on June 5.
OL,16,FThe cartoonist, who is best known for
OL,17,Fillustrating Roald Dahl's books,
OL,18,Fvisited the centre to unveil his new
OL,19,Fartwork A Bridge To The Past.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
