PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780207510
OL,3,CSir Quentin Blake unveils mural ahead
OL,4,Cof illustration centre opening
OL,6,F"Crossing it are folk in period
OL,7,Fcostume; they are all invented by me,
OL,8,Fexcept for the two men fishing who are
OL,9,Fborrowed from a print made in the
OL,10,F1700s."
OL,12,FThe mural shows figures drawn to the
OL,13,Friver through the ages, with the
OL,14,Fcartoonist taking inspiration from
OL,15,Fartwork by Scottish painter Isaac
OL,16,FCruikshank to illustrate men fishing
OL,17,Fin formal attire.
