OL,3,CSir Quentin Blake unveils mural ahead
OL,4,Cof illustration centre opening
OL,6,FSir Quentin established a charity for
OL,7,Fillustration in 2002 and set out to
OL,8,Fcreate the UK's first public venue
OL,9,Fdedicated to illustration.
OL,11,FOpening next month, the centre will
OL,12,Fpresent regularly changing exhibitions
OL,13,Fon illustration, across three
OL,14,Fgalleries. It will reportedly be the
OL,15,Fworld's largest space for illustration.
OL,17,FTo celebrate its opening, the centre
OL,18,Fwill be giving away free tickets to
OL,19,Fthe first 50 people to illustrate an
OL,20,Fofficial voucher collected on-site on
OL,21,Fopening day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
