OL,3,CSir Quentin Blake unveils mural ahead
OL,4,Cof illustration centre opening
OL,6,FA Bridge To The Past was created in
OL,7,Fink by Sir Quentin and has been scaled
OL,8,Fup to sit on the centre's cafe wall.
OL,10,FThe centre includes galleries, a free
OL,11,Fillustration library, gardens, a cafe
OL,12,Fand a shop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
